				                <div>Hello Christie,<br />
<br />
Thanks for the question and sorry for the problems with the email account.  Actually, I believe you're trying to set up a new @me accounts, which is no longer possible.  Apple has discontinued that domain for emails.  You can create a new account ending in .icloud - all Apple email accounts are based on individual AppleID accounts.  You need to <a href="https://appleid.apple.com/account" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">create an AppleID</a> and then you can use that with your chosen email client.  You can always setup a gmail account, but that is different from Apple's email account.  <br />
<br />
I hope this helps to clear up the problem.  Please let us know if you require any further assistance.<br />
<br />
